vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for an R-7.5(A) Single Family District on property zoned an R-10(A) Single Family District and NO(A) Neighborhood Office District, on the northeast corner of Greenville Avenue and Windy Crest Drive and an ordinance granting an R-10(A) Single Family District on the portion of the property currently zoned an NO(A) District
Recommendation of Staff and CPC:  Approval of an R-10(A) Single Family District on the portion of the property currently zoned an NO(A) District
Z201-169(CT)
